@meta
title: Checkout Roadmap
version: 0.1
owner: ai-agent
doc_base_path: 

@map
- RD-000 | Input Guide | Quick rules for what to fill in this document
- RD-001 | Vision | Define strategic direction and principles
- RD-010 | Quarterly Goals | Define quarter-level outcomes and done criteria
- RD-020 | Execution Plan | Break down execution by domain
- RD-030 | Metrics | Define success and risk metrics
- RD-040 | Risk Mitigation | Define top risks and mitigation plans

@section RD-000
title: Input Guide
{
	summary: Minimum input rules for consistent writing by humans and AI
	links: GUIDE-INPUT
	content:
	<<<
	[Required input]
	1) Fill every blank after -, 1), and : with concrete content.
	2) Use specific numbers, dates, owners, and evidence whenever possible.
	3) If unknown, do not leave blank; write TBD (needs confirmation).

	[AI request contract]
	- target_docs: actual file path
	- target_sections: section IDs or section paths
	- goal: why this change is needed (1-2 sentences)
	- constraints: scope/forbidden constraints
	- done: validation-based completion criteria

	[AI output contract]
	- Changed files / Changed sections / Reason / Impact / Risks / Validation

	[Done checklist]
	- Are @map rows and @section IDs aligned?
	- For edits, is @change reason/impact recorded?
	>>>
}

@section RD-001
title: Vision
{
	summary: Align teams around a clear direction
	links: VISION-001
	content:
	<<<
	[Problem space]
	- Current limitation:
	- Opportunity:

	[Principles]
	1)
	2)
	3)
	>>>
}

@section RD-010
title: Quarterly Goals
{
	summary: Define measurable goals per quarter
	links: OKR-001
	content:
	<<<
	Q1:
	- Goal:
	- Done criteria:

	Q2:
	- Goal:
	- Done criteria:

	Q3:
	- Goal:
	- Done criteria:
	>>>
}

